Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:07.13,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto of the Third Eye, a part \Nof the organization known as
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Eye of the Midnight Sun that \Nseeks to destroy the Clover Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.27,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,infiltrated the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:41.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His power was so great that Asta and the \Nothers fell to him, one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:49.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:53.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:58.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But Noelle diligently faced off with Vetto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:00:59.97,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,in order to protect her friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:03.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Noelle Silva of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:06.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt my friends and comrades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:10.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:35.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:39.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as though Noelle's attack \Nhad finally defeated Vetto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:42.43,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but the battle wasn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:49.27,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive... You managed \Nto draw me out, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.11,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:54.08,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.46,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! I'm going to go get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.03,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You two tend to as many people as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:25.83,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,What's this horrifying mana I'm sensing \Nfrom the bottom of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.39,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the beast from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:32.43,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is even worse. It's no beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.40,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's a monster that's way \Nmore powerful than a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:42.91,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What is this ominous mana? \NI've never felt anything like it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:49.20,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Does Lord Vetto's power concern you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:52.46,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,You must be buzzing with confidence, \Nto look away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:54.00,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.88,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the people \Nthe captain mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:00.11,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Third Eye, the strongest group \Nin the Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.89,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who infiltrated the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.60,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Sucks for you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:10.48,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be exterminated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.71,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to suck all the magic out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.65,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:21.91,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you and find my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.23,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The way he looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:35.58,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like one of the fairy tales \NGranny used to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:41.83,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, there were evil fiends \Nthat lived in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:48.27,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted to make this world \Nand all of its magic their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.61,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest among them used forbidden magic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:55.60,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,to turn himself into a \Ndemon of incredible power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.48,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to exterminate humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:04.56,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,The one who stood against him\Nlater became the first Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:10.37,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This man is just like one of \Nthe fiends from that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.68,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.48,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.70,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.67,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That last spell drained all my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:20.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:24.23,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet? Yes, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:29.91,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now is when I show you true despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:06.78,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}The Only Weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:17.19,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you planning to do? \NYou can't leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:20.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave them alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.46,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,Useless, useless, it's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.07,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:35.46,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever escaped my Spatial Magic:\N Different Dimension Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:41.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Hurry up and let me \Nout of here, or you'll be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.16,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:49.67,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, well, aren't you scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat the shit out of you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! It's too late to apologize now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.17,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.89,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this guy is violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:21.51,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito Magic: Mosquito Hum!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:34.18,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell? You're trying\Nto suck blood from a stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.73,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This sound's going to make me go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:50.95,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? It's like\Nyou've suffered a painful bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:56.74,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito Magic: Mana-Sucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.81,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how long you \Ncan keep buzzing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.59,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to destroy you Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:17.01,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,so that we, the Eye of the Midnight \NSun, can fulfill our great desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.97,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Not able to run anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.65,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,M-My arm won't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:36.36,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just your arm that won't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.54,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:46.00,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for moving closer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If you were too far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.47,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,my threads would've been \Nblown away by the sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:56.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I? That I was going to \Ndefeat you and go to my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.43,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.80,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thread Magic: Dancing Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:08.34,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body's bugging out on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.56,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:14.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Suck up as much magic as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:17.36,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll have to settle for your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:26.33,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,M-My magic's... being sucked away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:38.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness. I'm going to replenish \Nall the mana that was wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.89,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:58.85,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can still stand,\Nanti-magic brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.20,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,But it's futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.11,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do when you're so beat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.77,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing mana
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:13.12,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,whispers to me that I should show you \Nvermin what true despair looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... You're badly hurt. How did you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:23.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono... used the last of \Nher strength to heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:25.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,With a faint song...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:57.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pulverize this guy and heal \Nboth Kahono's throat and Kiato's leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:58.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even he managed to regrow an arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:06.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's someone out there \Nwho can use magic to heal them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:13.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That insane spell you did earlier... \NIt helped me get back onto my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:20.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as awesome as I thought you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:31.47,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, nope, nope, \Nnope, nope, nope, nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:33.94,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.49,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, nope, nope, \Nnope, nope, nope, nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.05,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:49.87,italics,Final,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to you? \NLook how beat up you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.33,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.51,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Especially against a monster like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.35,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.27,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:01.40,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They are the strongest three \Nin the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.73,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:08.53,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... In combat, they surpass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.91,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.62,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,They're more powerful than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.25,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Third Eye, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:19.08,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He has to be bluffing when he says \Nthey're stronger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.38,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.49,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He does have much stronger magic than Licht,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.28,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,the leader of the Eye of the Midnight Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:30.59,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we could beat this guy,\Neven if we ganged up on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.01,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is already down for the count...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.35,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And he made this giant \Nhole with no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.01,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I'm going to escape through that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.61,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! There's no way I can save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:53.86,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I need to at least escape,\Nor we'll all be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.46,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, how pathetic you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:00.21,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do in that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:04.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't get cocky just \Nbecause you got another eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.72,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, nope, nope, nope, nope, \Nnope, nope! That guy's totally right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:12.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, this is impossible! \NThat guy's magic is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.10,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.18,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry up and run! \NNo, seriously, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:22.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned earlier that one of my \Nweak points is that I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:27.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:30.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my only weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:35.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm never going to give \Nup until I fulfill my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.91,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:53.72,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you just how \Nuseless that weapon is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:59.18,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you exactly what despair means!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:05.91,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Before I defeat you lot, I should \Nprobably take out the trash first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:07.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.28,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:39.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear... Big and hairy over there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:43.47,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,must be the insane guy named Vetto \Nthe captain was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:47.23,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're way more ugly than I thought you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.98,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should've just passed out drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:02.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But you really are insane, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.90,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.02,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't give up, and that's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:11.59,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and pull me along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why the other \NBlack Bulls liked you so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.91,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,and I think I finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:26.60,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, kid.\NJust like what Vanessa said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:31.11,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Because you didn't give up, Noelle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.69,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.86,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Magna, and Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:39.37,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,were all able to go beyond their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.74,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And... me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:50.34,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,A heart that refuses to \Ngive up is your only weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.37,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.88,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think that these cobwebs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.18,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,could keep a beast like me tied down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:03.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What fun would it be if you \Nactually stayed tied down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:04.81,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:10.93,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly think you can defeat me just \Nbecause another insect joined your cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.40,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:17.91,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:27.12,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,So there was still another mouse hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.58,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:33.17,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:39.05,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My juniors are working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That means I have to\Nact like a proper senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:46.18,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! What the heck am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.10,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:52.61,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you actually showed up.\NGood job, Finral the wuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:57.78,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I showed up! \NI'm no wuss, Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.28,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up! Don't give up! \NDon't give up! Don't give up! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.12,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You vermin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:10.29,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're ants. Less than vermin. \NNo matter how many of you gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.92,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,you won't even be able to scratch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:16.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, you have enough magic \Nto protect everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:17.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:26.23,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Still... his magic is unbelievable. Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:28.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.75,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I can't see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:35.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I definitely feel his ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:40.07,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If he manages to hit us head-on with any \Nof his attacks, it'll instantly be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's life or death right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.86,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts, damn it! I want to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.96,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If we get out of this alive, \NI'll give you a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.33,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A hug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:54.96,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You can cry all you want right into my bosom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.96,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral's ki just blew the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:04.63,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling guys is child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:09.47,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And for you, ordinary magic attacks \Nwon't work on him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You and your anti-magic will \Njust have to take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.48,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't let go of \Nthat sword, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:19.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Go give it all you've got. \NPut your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:25.70,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that we won't let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:35.33,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.84,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.22,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:05.47,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,My long-range attacks never \Neven touch the anti-magic sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.95,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The spatial magic user just \Nsends them right back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:13.21,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,For a mere human,\Nhe's quite fast and accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:16.32,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.21,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But I've gotta do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.21,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.96,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to pick \Nthem off at close range!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.68,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:40.73,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the spatial magic and\Nyour aura are gushing all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:45.86,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.78,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The thread changed his trajectory...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:54.39,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You scuttling little insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,with this weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:55.41,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:54.59,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:58.91,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Service Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:58.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Service Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:01.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's service magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:04.54,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Just like it sounds, it's magic \Nthat's a service to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:06.22,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:07.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:10.38,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All we've had lately is smelly \Nand hairy guys like Vetto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:12.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,hogging up all the screen time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:14.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:21.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So this is service magic!\NI wonder how Mimosa's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:24.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! That was a total success!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:26.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those perfect bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:29.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... The Black Bulls—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:32.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?! Stupidsta, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:34.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:38.23,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to work \Ntogether and defeat Vetto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.43,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Finral and I will assist you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:43.36,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able... no, \NI know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:47.31,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 48: "Despair vs. Hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:50.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 48\N\N{\fs18}Despair vs. Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.31,0:23:49.84,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is our magic!
